UMKM Fishing Management System (CLI - C)

This project is a simple CLI-based application developed using C to assist in managing administrative activities for a fishing UMKM business.

📌 Description
The system is designed to help manage basic operations such as recording data and handling simple transactions. It was built as a team project to simulate a real-world management system in a small-scale business.

⚙️ Features
- Input and manage data
- Record simple transactions
- Display information through CLI interface
- Basic menu navigation system

🛠️ Tech Stack
- C Programming Language
- CLI (Command Line Interface)

👥 Project Role
This project was developed as a team project.  
I contributed as a **team lead**, guiding the development process, helping structure the program, and focusing on debugging and improving code stability.

🎯 Purpose
The main goal of this project is to understand basic system design, program logic, and how simple applications can be used to support small businesses.

🚀 Future Improvements
- Improve user interface (better CLI interaction)
- Add more features and data validation
- Optimize code structure
